one has been so helpful so far that I'm hopeful that we will. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=vampiricmuse>Vampiric Muse</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Zsu - What? You thought I would stay dead? </span><br>  Posts: 377<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(7/27/03 9:02 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm9.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1788.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://cobra.xprofile.net/userimages/9099757754588853.gif height=176 width=100></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Can you help this cat?</span><hr size=1> Dalion didn't want this done, but since he did such a nice thing I wanted to post.<br>
